https://news.opensuse.org/2023/06/07/leap-release-matures-sets-up-tech-transition/ Leap 15.5 版本成熟，开启技术转型Wed, 07 Jun 2023 12:00:00 +0000 https://news.opensuse.org/2023/06/07/leap-release-matures-sets-up-tech-transition/ admin@opensuse.org（道格拉斯·德马约）  EN / CA / CS / DE / ES / FR / JA / NL / ZH-TW 德国纽伦堡 – openSUSE 最新 15 系列版本的发布标志着五年多前开始的多年维护和安全工作。 Leap 15.5 的成熟发挥了新的作用...... <p>;<a href="https://news.opensuse.org/2023/06/07/leap-release-matures-sets-up-tech-transition/">;EN</a>; / <a href= “https://en.opensuse.org/Anunci_de_la_versi%C3%B3_15.5">;CA</a>; / <a href="http://cs.opensuse.org/Ozn%C3%A1men%C3%AD_nov %C3%A9ho_vyd%C3%A1n%C3%AD_15.5">;CS</a>; / <a href="https://de.opensuse.org/Release_announcement_15.5">;DE</a>; / <a href="http://es.opensuse.org/Anuncio_publicaci%C3%B3n_15.5">;ES</a>; / <a href="http://fr.opensuse.org/Annonce_de_version_15.5">;FR< /a>; / <a href="http://ja.opensuse.org/%E3%83%AA%E3%83%AA%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B9%E3%82%A2% E3%83%8A%E3%82%A6%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B9_15.5">;JA</a>; / <a href="http://nl.opensuse.org/Aankondiging_van_uitgave_van_15。 5">;NL</a>; / <a href="http://zh-tw.opensuse.org/Release_announcement_15.5">;ZH-TW</a>;</p>; <p>;德国纽伦堡 – <a href="https://get.opensuse.org">;openSUSE</a>; 最新 15 系列版本的发布标志着五年多前开始的多年维护和安全工作。</p>; <p >; 随着过去五年新技术变革的引入，<a href="https://get.opensuse.org/leap/15.5/">;Leap 15.5</a>; 的成熟度开始发挥作用，例如容器技术、不可变系统、虚拟化、嵌入式开发和其他高科技进步。</p>; <p>;企业家、爱好者、专业人士和开发人员使用 Leap 作为首选 Linux 发行版，如 <a href="https 所示://metrics.opensuse.org/">;每个次要版本的使用量增加</a>;。从遗留软件过渡到更现代的系统迫在眉睫。</p>; <p>;<a href="https://get.opensuse.org/leap/15.5/">;Leap 15.5</a>;，它基于<a href="https://www.suse.com/products/server/">;SUSE Linux Enterprise 15</a>; Service Pack 5，将在 2024 年底之前收到维护和安全更新。这将为用户提供有足够的时间过渡到该版本的后续版本；继任者尚未确定。对商业支持感兴趣的用户可以使用<a href="https://en.opensuse.org/SDB:How_to_migrate_to_SLE">;新工具</a>;过渡到商业支持。 Leap 可以在 <a href="https://get.opensuse.org">;get.opensuse.org</a>; 下载。</p>; <p>;此版本带来了更新的软件包，例如 <a href="https ://www.mesa3d.org/">;Mesa</a>; 等，但 <a href="https://get.opensuse.org/leap/15.5/">;Leap 15.5</a>; 不是一个- 功能发布。其中一些需要强调的较新软件包包括 KDE <a href="https://kde.org/announcements/plasma/5/5.27.0/">;Plasma 5.27</a>;，这是 Plasma 长期支持版本，直到下一个版本将于 2024 年推出。 <a href="https://community.kde.org/Konqi">;Konqi</a>; 爱好者将享受新的欢迎向导、桌面工作区的动态自定义以及更多功能 <a href="https://userbase.kde.org/Plasma/Krunner">;KRunner</a>; 包括完整的桌面搜索、单位和货币汇率转换、字典定义、计算器功能，并显示数学的图形表示功能。颜色选择器进行了一些改进，并添加了显示另一个预览色环的可能性。 <a href="https://kde.org/announcements/gear/22.12.3/">;KDE Gear 22.12.3</a>; 将是该版本中的一个新软件包，并补充 <a href=" https://kde.org/announcements/plasma/5/5.27.0/">;Plasma 5.27</a>;。此更新修复了桌面环境应用程序的错误，并突出显示了压缩/解压缩实用程序 <a href="https://apps.kde.org/ark/">;ark</a>; 的增强、文本编辑器的改进<a href ="https://apps.kde.org/kate/">;Kate</a>; 并修复了视频编辑器的一些崩溃<a href="https://apps.kde.org/kdenlive/">;Kdenlive< /a>;. Qt 5.15 LTS 可通过 <a href="https://dot.kde.org/2021/04/06/announcing-kdes-qt-5-patch-collection">;KDE Qt 5 补丁集合</a>;获取.</p>; <p>;文本编辑器 <a href="https://www.vim.org/">;Vim</a>; 将升级到新的主要版本。 <a href="https://www.vim.org/">;Vim</a>; 9 有一种新的脚本语言，可以极大地提高性能。 Increases in execution speed of 10 to 100 times is expected for the text editor. Users are recommended to read the project's <a href="https://www.vim.org/vim90.php">;Vim 9.0 release information</a>; to know how the upgrade affects legacy scripts, backwards compatibility and other new features added in the release.</p>; <p>;For professionals configuring networking of Linux containers, the <a href="https://github.com/containers/netavark">;netavark</a>; 1.5.0 package is in the release. Users who have already transitioned to <a href="https://flatpak.org/">;Flatpaks</a>; will have an updated <a href="https://github.com/flatpak/flatpak/releases/tag/1.14.4">;1.14.4</a>; version that addresses a <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Common_Vulnerabilities_and_Exposures">;Common Vulnerability and Exposure</a>; with <a href="https://github.com/flatpak/flatpak/security/advisories/GHSA-h43h-fwqx-mpp8">;CVE-2023-28101</a>;. The newer version fixes the hiding of permissions for an attacker publishing a Flatpak app with malicious intent to elevate permissions.</p>; <p>;Leap 15.5 is set to have the <a href="https://en.opensuse.org/OpenH264">;OpenH264</a>; repository enabled by default for all new installations thanks to contributions from <a href="https://eti.cisco.com/open-source">;Open Source at Cisco</a>;.</p>; <p>;Leap 15.5 comes with <a href="https://www.kernel.org/">;Linux Kernel</a>; 5.14.21 that including backports for this SUSE specific LTS kernel. Leap 15.5 shares the kernel with SLE 15 SP5 that receives the same fixes and backports along, which includes a few thousand other shared packages. The device firmware updater package <a href="https://github.com/fwupd/fwupd">;fwupd</a>; will change to version 1.8.6. The newer version fixes compiling errors when building for <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/IBM_System/390">;s390x</a>; and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ppc64">;ppc64le</a>;</p>; <p>;Good news for Python developers. Leap 15.5 users will have a fully usable Python 3.11 stack in parallel to the system Python (python36). This provides a more modern release for users and developers. Packagers are advised to switch to Python 3.11.</p>; <p>;Other packages users may notice a change to are updates of <a href="https://github.com/Genivia/ugrep">;Ugrep</a>; 3.11.0 and <a href="https://networkmanager.dev/">;NetworkManager</a>; 1.38.6. Both <a href="https://webkitgtk.org/">;webkit2gtk3</a>; and <a href="https://webkitgtk.org/">;webkit2gtk4</a>; will update to version 2.38.5. <a href="https://www.mozilla.org/">;Mozilla</a>;'s internet browser <a href="https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/new/">;Firefox</a>; will get a new Extended Support Release version - 102.9.0. <a href="https://www.mozilla.org/">;Mozilla</a>;'s email client <a href="https://www.thunderbird.net/en-US/thunderbird/102.8.0/releasenotes/">;Thunderbird</a>; gains various visual and user experience improvements with version 102.8.0.</p>; <h3 id="end-of-life">;End of Life</h3>; <p>;openSUSE Leap 15.4 will have its End of Life (EOL) six months from today's release. Users should update to openSUSE Leap 15.5 within six months of today to continue to receive security and maintenance updates.</p>; <h3 id="important-for-users-upgrading-from-previous-versions">;Important for users upgrading from previous versions</h3>; <p>;A new 4096-bit RSA signing key was introduced as part of openSUSE Leap 15.5 as well as 15.4 via a maintenance update. Leap 15.4 users are expected to update their system prior to upgrade of 15.5. For more information, visit <a href="https://en.opensuse.org/SDB:System_upgrade#0._New_4096_bit_RSA_signing_key">;https://en.opensuse.org/SDB:System_upgrade#0._New_4096_bit_RSA_signing_key</a>;</p>; <h3 id="download-leap-155">;Download Leap 15.5</h3>; <p>;To download the ISO image, visit <a href="https://get.opensuse.org/leap/">;https://get.opensuse.org/leap/</a>;</p>; <h3 id="questions">;Questions</h3>; <p>;If you have a question about the release or found a bug, we'd love to hear from you at:</p>; <p>;<a href="https://t.me/openSUSE">;https://t.me/openSUSE</a>;</p>; <p>;<a href="https://chat.opensuse.org">;https://chat.opensuse.org</a>;</p>; <p>;<a href="https://lists.opensuse.org/opensuse-support/">;https://lists.opensuse.org/opensuse-support/</a>;</p>; <p>;<a href="https://discordapp.com/invite/openSUSE">;https://discordapp.com/invite/openSUSE</a>;</p>; <p>;<a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/opensuseproject">;https://www.facebook.com/groups/opensuseproject</a>;</p>; <h3 id="get-involved">;Get involved</h3>; <p>;The openSUSE Project is a worldwide community that promotes the use of Linux everywhere. It creates two of the world's best Linux distributions, the Tumbleweed rolling-release, and Leap, the hybrid enterprise-community distribution. openSUSE is continuously working together in an open, transparent and friendly manner as part of the worldwide Free and Open Source Software community. The project is controlled by its community and relies on the contributions of individuals, working as testers, writers, translators, usability experts, artists and ambassadors or developers. The project embraces a wide variety of technology, people with different levels of expertise, speaking different languages and having different cultural backgrounds. Learn more about it on <a href="https://opensuse.org">;opensuse.org</a>;.</p>; <meta name="openSUSE, SUSE, Leap, SLE, Enterprise, Linux, RSA Key, python, xfce, kde, vim, flatpak, openh264" content="HTML,CSS,XML,JavaScript" />;
